  </developer>
  <description>
    <p>
      A GTK mail-merge emailing app for small business offering:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Email personalization</li>
      <li>Email attachments</li>
      <li>HTML and text emails</li>
      <li>CSV recipient data import</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
